<body>
    <h1>Send SMS</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"125a1fe0b6c8"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"2dddb7934683"><strong>Category:</strong> Messaging</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"546099a3857a" id=3D"SendSMS-Overview">Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3ed325391021">The <strong>Send SMS</strong> action sends an =
SMS message to a guest's phone number. The message can be sent on behalf of=
 the hotel or the guest, and can optionally be linked to a reservation. Thi=
s is useful for automating guest communication as part of a workflow =E2=80=
=94 for example, sending a welcome message when a reservation is confirmed,=
 or notifying a guest about a room upgrade.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6fb09cd9ae14">The recipient guest can be specified directly =
via their Guest ID, or resolved automatically from a Reservation ID. At lea=
st one of these two fields must be provided. When the SMS is sent successfu=
lly, the component signals completion on the <strong>out</strong> port, all=
owing the workflow to continue to the next step.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"90f11255-484e-4b4c-b6b9-e08a4e93015a">
<h2 local-id=3D"6e40336c08f3" id=3D"SendSMS-InputFields">Input Fields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"99d5cb39-112d-4b67-9bbe-91e=
39d8ab4ca" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e6995fa2-bae0-4609-b602-13146cf25c95">
<th data-local-id=3D"748c63d0-f86b-45b5-9d90-7515bd7a7430" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"623409effc07">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"521fb8f2-e1fc-40b1-9131-31eb796f14bd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"38fccf2dea14">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ce988c59-f2fc-4fc2-bba1-a5cc1042990e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"93d50e7e64ab">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8f5fead1-6fb5-4b54-ad5d-4ba86ac47c1e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8c742f997fe5">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f7f9e42f-c0c6-464d-9f0e-f8dca682f0a3">
<td data-local-id=3D"7fe0a358-12da-49b8-bbf1-3d15de1d059b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0af67323ad94"><strong>Guest ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1bdd7077-6b05-49f5-9f6c-34097c77647d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a3b2db60df0"><strong>Conditional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"47616af2-04ac-4f7d-8bf5-1eda3bcf4993" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fb69032db0e1">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"803f806f-6e0f-4d21-b489-a43726c664a2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c3326c880a9c">The unique identifier of the guest to send the=
 SMS to. If provided, the SMS is sent directly to this guest and the Reserv=
ation ID is only used to link the message to the reservation. If not provid=
ed, the guest is resolved automatically from the Reservation ID.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9177627a-79bd-417c-b862-410bf23e380d">
<td data-local-id=3D"15a24c12-059c-4b73-960c-153b92001d7a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ac58dd784b44"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4ad0956f-7e1c-4bc3-96c1-f8607d21fd34" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"24349cd5c9eb"><strong>Conditional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ae63b569-f410-44a7-a410-feb51b7eaf69" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7e5350b97ac6">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3b3328f7-c087-4283-bc83-198a9ab7cee6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0751fce0289f">The unique identifier of a reservation. If Gue=
st ID is not provided, the guest is resolved from this reservation. If Gues=
t ID is provided, the reservation is only used to link the SMS to it. Typic=
ally populated dynamically from a previous step in the workflow (e.g., a tr=
igger that provides a reservation ID).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e0105ea6-88b7-49e1-b71c-e6f875a02907">
<td data-local-id=3D"0eda3675-1e72-4c8b-8b19-09acc78060a0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fe57a5e9db2b"><strong>Message body</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b5589a85-7d0c-4d56-8a99-0b4184ea50d9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c1ae2ca65b4f"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4d04c4e0-00a3-4c7a-ad58-9affca4d3e19" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0651b631bf3f">Text (multiline)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a308ee7e-3311-4ce5-94be-f48db1373a5c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bc4709f5607d">The text content of the SMS message to send. T=
his field cannot be empty or whitespace-only.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9ce71f7f-f58f-4caf-bc77-949c65b9944c">
<td data-local-id=3D"b7cc8953-b7a3-4f25-a167-ad30eca3c9d4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b501332cbc35"><strong>Sender</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4b34e06a-e312-4f1c-bd32-eb9d9c17c107" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82ac0a0231d6"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2c58f141-69c8-4e89-b9cd-96748ea7cd47" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"24411f75ae39">Dropdown (select)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4b7944f4-59ae-4148-8150-0c508705fd7d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3212a93a06bf">Determines who the message is sent on behalf o=
f. Options:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"07356154-2cf5-467c-ba6d-c97f50e74f09">
<li local-id=3D"bf16a559-1e66-4f3b-8b45-480fe9c357b6">
<p local-id=3D"dbef4ccdd519"><strong>Hotel</strong> (default) =E2=80=94 The=
 SMS is sent on behalf of the hotel.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a5cd58e-6573-49e4-a08a-4acb58564c7b">
<p local-id=3D"8ca08fb7e62e"><strong>Guest</strong> =E2=80=94 The SMS is se=
nt on behalf of the guest.</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e2bb4b321ec7"><strong>Important:</strong> At least one of <s=
trong>Guest ID</strong> or <strong>Reservation ID</strong> must be provided=
. If neither is supplied, the action will fail with a validation error.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a2682fa2015f"><strong>Note:</strong> When both <strong>Guest=
 ID</strong> and <strong>Reservation ID</strong> are provided, the SMS is s=
ent to the specified guest and the reservation is used only to associate th=
e message with that reservation. When only <strong>Reservation ID</strong> =
is provided, the guest is automatically looked up from the reservation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"32d60ec7-969b-4a11-972f-07b2a2d3a009">
<h2 local-id=3D"741827f45c70" id=3D"SendSMS-Output">Output</h2>
<p local-id=3D"716c263f696c">When the SMS is sent successfully, the compone=
nt signals completion on the <strong>out</strong> output port. This port do=
es not carry additional data fields =E2=80=94 it serves as a signal that th=
e message was sent, allowing subsequent steps in the workflow to proceed.</=
p>
<hr local-id=3D"d6d4ba91-edc7-4033-aaf6-8f4179ca43d8">
<h2 local-id=3D"f06c32fee5d2" id=3D"SendSMS-HowItWorks">How It Works</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d6f27a66-acba-49cd-8216-f2e32a733786">
<li local-id=3D"db8005ea-0ed8-410b-8358-c05e7bad1efc">
<p local-id=3D"978f9df64433">The component receives input values from the p=
revious step in the workflow (or from manually configured values).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"245ecf82-5b6d-4f65-8d81-107aaf8ed1c3">
<p local-id=3D"68ed177bbe3f">It validates that at least one of <strong>Gues=
t ID</strong> or <strong>Reservation ID</strong> is provided and that the <=
strong>Message body</strong> is not empty.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"437ea962-ceff-42b2-978d-45d19271c814">
<p local-id=3D"8f1430e1730f">If <strong>Guest ID</strong> is not provided, =
the system looks up the guest associated with the given <strong>Reservation=
 ID</strong>. If no matching reservation is found, the action fails with an=
 error.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13e27ef3-52cc-4649-b8e0-93cea3745291">
<p local-id=3D"b523b4fd441a">The SMS is sent to the resolved guest via the =
Mews messaging service, using the specified <strong>Sender</strong> and opt=
ionally linking the message to the reservation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d32ed442-b441-4318-95b5-474320aacf9b">
<p local-id=3D"e90c773c8a37">If the SMS is sent successfully, the <strong>o=
ut</strong> port is triggered, allowing the workflow to continue.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a36eb2b8-dd6a-4144-abe6-954d4fe6ae95">
<p local-id=3D"bbc338b5e9ac">If the sending fails (e.g., due to an invalid =
guest, a service issue, or an empty message body), the component returns an=
 error.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"70366f59-bd99-45e9-808a-f79e66270fa4">
<h2 local-id=3D"6b33f5347c6f" id=3D"SendSMS-ExampleUseCases">Example Use Ca=
ses</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"250b3afb-a566-4d0c-a015-85ff8b555743">
<li local-id=3D"7232207a-1e34-4b95-9372-12f7bafba7d0">
<p local-id=3D"1189b3b5fc1c"><strong>Welcome message</strong> =E2=80=94 Whe=
n a reservation is confirmed, automatically send a welcome SMS to the guest=
 with check-in instructions or property information.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a1f8d8b-46aa-4260-a8d4-d0cb83dd8fcd">
<p local-id=3D"c8dcbd73f745"><strong>Room upgrade notification</strong> =E2=
=80=94 After upgrading a guest's room, send an SMS informing them of the up=
grade details.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1274c4e4-be85-4458-8e6f-ccb400699fa4">
<p local-id=3D"e2598001f57e"><strong>Check-out reminder</strong> =E2=80=94 =
On the day of departure, send a reminder SMS to the guest with check-out ti=
me and instructions.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74e80082-e7eb-4112-af06-5e62dbd7f160">
<p local-id=3D"1342ee3313aa"><strong>Custom communication</strong> =E2=80=
=94 Use dynamic message content from previous workflow steps to send person=
alized messages based on guest preferences or reservation details.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3695c18d-0737-4349-aee1-3c306125dd62">
<h2 local-id=3D"ab0afbe50911" id=3D"SendSMS-ErrorHandling">Error Handling</=
h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d975f2dd-817d-4204-902a-028=
3953f112c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"46e2d4d4-3209-427d-a5a6-c63289a8365d">
<th data-local-id=3D"fa5f1248-c16f-41c3-8eae-6ca979547337" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"650e7fc7085e">Error</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"29dcadde-d3d4-41e5-a5de-940fd6f29ab3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"49fc62ec6401">Cause</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9e840387-e7ff-4c4d-94bc-8d82760c0e6f">
<td data-local-id=3D"09e92da9-fa3c-4ffc-abd4-e09f06a86d4b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b53e2cf6d57"><code>At least one of GuestId or ReservationId=
 must be provided.</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"66f95bf8-8c2e-4a6b-b9da-93e4110ba7b7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74c2b9bc5e37">Neither Guest ID nor Reservation ID was suppli=
ed. Provide at least one of the two fields.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"86cc1bb0-902f-4857-a3fc-9f14f111b480">
<td data-local-id=3D"6f99c1fa-adf6-417b-99a6-632d8e2cfc7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e6717d11e283"><code>Reservation not found.</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"beea9502-da24-4425-ad54-c7eed1ac0d09" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f340ebe769e2">The provided Reservation ID does not match any=
 existing reservation in the property. Verify the reservation ID is correct=
.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b5ae9ac6-68ee-42d2-b64e-fba5a77e426d">
<td data-local-id=3D"9ff9ce27-2f39-4d65-9c21-4ff3b7a83327" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f0f1931d4980"><code>Body is required.</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b42ec253-7095-4306-b14b-550e8c1f2856" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"733d0b3ac706">The Message body field was left empty or conta=
ins only whitespace.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"513a55fa-ba74-4b3b-89c2-cac2bc6386b6">
<td data-local-id=3D"424c7680-72b1-4b1e-80d5-e713fd47b93d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6837b719adb7"><code>An error occurred while sending the SMS.=
</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7a0dac7f-9aa2-4232-9f03-37c025eaffcf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9cd90f970b46">The request to the messaging service failed. T=
his may indicate a temporary service issue or a problem with the guest's co=
ntact information.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
------=_Part_40_1085244166.1777536584195--
